    </li>
</ul>
<h3>
    Best Baits and Lures
</h3>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Drift Fishing</strong>: Yarnies, roe, pink worms, beads
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Float Fishing</strong>: Jigs tipped with shrimp or worms
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Spinners/Spoons</strong>: Blue Fox, Panther Martin, Little Cleo
    </li>
</ul>
<h3>
    Fishing Techniques
</h3>
<ul>
